{
  "sequence": [
    {
      "subject": "Congrats on Acme's new AI platform, Jane!",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI saw Acme's recent AI platform launch – impressive work! At LeadCraft, we help product teams like yours accelerate adoption through data‑driven outreach. Would you be open to a brief call to explore synergies?\n\nBest,\n[Your Name]"
    },
    {
      "subject": "Building on our AI conversation",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nFollowing up on my previous email – we’ve helped companies such as BetaTech achieve a 30% increase in demo bookings after their AI rollouts. I’ve attached a one‑pager with relevant case studies. Let me know if you’d like to discuss further.\n\nRegards,\n[Your Name]"
    },
    {
      "subject": "Last try – AI‑driven outreach for Acme",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI understand you’re busy. If timing isn’t right, feel free to let me know a better window. Otherwise, I’m happy to share a quick snapshot of how our AI‑enhanced sequences could boost Acme’s product adoption.\n\nThanks,\n[Your Name]"
    }
  ]
}
